Say '''Vallehermoso''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Negros Oriental]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 36,943 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 101.25 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumatlo ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6224.	
															
